==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Dispunge
<hw>Dis*punge"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>dispungere</ets> to prick apart, <it>i. e.</it>, check off the
debts and credits of an account; <ets>dis-</ets> + <ets>pungere</ets> to
prick.]</ety> <def>To expunge; to erase.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Dispunge</ent>⟦br⟧

